### 1. 獲取分類樹
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/categories
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>

### 2. 創建頂級分類
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>

{
  "name": "電子產品",
  "parentId": null,
  "sortOrder": 0,
  "isActive": true
}

### 3. 創建子分類
POST http://localhost:3000/api/admin/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>

{
  "name": "手機",
  "parentId": "<parent-category-id>",
  "sortOrder": 0,
  "isActive": true
}

### 4. 獲取分類詳情
GET http://localhost:3000/api/admin/categories/<category-id>
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>

### 5. 更新分類
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/categories/<category-id>
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>

{
  "name": "更新後的分類名稱",
  "isActive": false
}

### 6. 重新排序分類
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/categories/<category-id>/reorder
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>

{
  "newSortOrder": 1
}

### 7. 移動分類
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/categories/<category-id>/move
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>

{
  "newParentId": "<new-parent-id>"
}

### 8. 批量操作
PATCH http://localhost:3000/api/admin/categories
Content-Type: application/json
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>

{
  "ids": ["<category-id-1>", "<category-id-2>"],
  "operation": "activate"
}

### 9. 刪除分類（軟刪除）
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/admin/categories/<category-id>
Authorization: Bearer <admin-token>